## Frequently Asked Questions

**Q: Do I need prior CAD or 3D printing experience?**  
A: No. We teach everything from scratch. Prior experience helps but isn't required.

**Q: Can I customize my aircraft for a specific mission?**  
A: Absolutely. Days 2-4 focus on mission-specific modifications. Bring your payload requirements.

**Q: What if my aircraft doesn't fly well on Day 8?**  
A: We build troubleshooting and tuning into the curriculum. Instructor works with you until it flies correctly.

**Q: Can I bring my own laptop/tools?**  
A: Yes, encouraged. We provide computers and tools, but you're welcome to use your own.

**Q: Is this course ITAR-restricted?**  
A: No. All content is export-controlled at EAR99 or lower. International students welcome (with proper documentation).

**Q: Do you offer group discounts?**  
A: Yes. Contact us for pricing on 5+ students from the same organization.

**Q: What if I can't complete the assessment?**  
A: You receive a detailed feedback report and can return for re-assessment within 6 months (discounted rate).

